  "texts": [
    "Incorporating these context would make for valuable future work, allowing for models that more closely emulate the decision process used by human misinformation annotators.",
    "At present, however, this lies outside the scope of this project.",
    "In general, the deployment of misinformation detectors comes with legal and ethical issues.",
    "Pre-emptive moderating of communication, which is typically the implicit goal of automated misinformation classifiers, is in essence a prior restraint on speech, regardless of the accuracy or OoD robustness of the model (Llansó 2020).",
    "While OoD robustness mitigates the propensity of such human rights violations (Tobi 2024), it cannot remove it entirely."
  ],
